Package: fidolasen
Type: Package
Title: FInd, DOwnload and preprocess LAndsat and SENtinel images
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person("Luigi", "Ranghetti", email = "ranghetti.l@irea.cnr.it", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Lorenzo", "Busetto", email = "lbusett@gmail.com", role = c("aut")))
Description: This package contains useful functions to preprocess Landsat and Sentinel-2 imagery.
  The download and the atmospheric correction is done using a python module (s2download).
  This package is under construction.
